# Copy to .env for local Expo tooling if needed. Do NOT put Gemini/Google keys here for the chatbot.
# CareBot: set GEMINI_API_KEY only on the Windows/Laragon server. See server-examples/GEMINI_CHATBOT_SETUP.md
# Optional on server: GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-2.5-flash-lite (repo PHP default; override if your key uses another id).

# PRODUCTION ONLY (set this in your hosting provider's dashboard, e.g. Vercel
# Project Settings -> Environment Variables). Leave unset for local dev -
# constants/api.ts falls back to Laragon/localhost automatically.
# Value = your Railway backend URL, no trailing slash, no "/carelink_api" suffix:
# EXPO_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://carelink-api-production.up.railway.app
